
// Write a Hyperlambda snippet that handles file read errors using a try/catch/finally block.

// Handles file read errors inside a try/catch/finally block
try

   // Attempting to read a non-existent file
   file.read:/invalid/path/to/file.txt
.catch

   // Logging the error
   log.error:x:@.arguments/*/message
.finally

   // Logging completion
   log.info:File read attempt finished
